{"tid":1896010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(被送中既下場) 桂民海寧波遭重判 涉為境外提供情報罪囚10年","createTime":"2020-02-25T01:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T07:06:18.000Z","uid":522,"like":35,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ff7ac93e9276acbe4caf63ae89442eebcbb338","tid":1896010,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/OSzhaE6KwJ_p9Mm0jPROZMRRrfA=/707x397/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/X7NNKAOVLWY6HP2AQS3ROIZO2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FOSzhaE6KwJ_p9Mm0jPROZMRRrfA%3D%2F707x397%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FX7NNKAOVLWY6HP2AQS3ROIZO2Y.jpg&h=8b243da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國浙江寧波法院在官公佈消息，香港銅鑼灣書店股東桂民海（又名桂敏海）上月遭起訴「為境外非法提供情報罪」，已於昨天「公開宣判」罪名成立，判處有期徒刑10年，剝奪政治權利5年。聲明稱，桂民海表示認罪服判不上訴。<br />\n<br />\n寧波法院通報稱，「充份保障了桂敏海依法享有的各項訴訟權利」，且有「部份社會群眾旁聽了宣判」。不過法院並未提供公開宣判的影片或其他相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200225/I4WEA4NLT656WQWG63OYJXIUSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200225%2FI4WEA4NLT656WQWG63OYJXIUSM%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=8a666ea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200225%2FI4WEA4NLT656WQWG63OYJXIUSM%2F&h=8d173106\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200225/I4WEA4NLT656WQWG63OYJXIUSM/</a>"},{"pid":"a00681c1bca035ccda4da4a220c9691b675ab22f","tid":1896010,"uid":125168,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"中共要搞你做瑞典人都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1437c438324296f1a4b04e60191a8eb754c8cd","tid":1896010,"uid":70745,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"cit